OL,5, The owner and former chairman of       
OL,6, Fleetwood Town FC has been jailed for a
OL,7, multi-million pound fraud which "duped"
OL,8, firms into expensive energy contracts. 
OL,10,FA trading standards investigation found
OL,11,FAndy Pilley mis-sold gas and           
OL,12,Felectricity contracts and posted fake  
OL,13,Fcustomer comments on websites.         
OL,15,FPilley, 53, of Thornton-Cleveleys,     
OL,16,FLancashire, resigned as chairman and   
OL,17,Fclub director of the League One side   
OL,18,Ffollowing his conviction last month.   
OL,20,FHe was jailed for 13 years.            
